        <div class="container info-container">
            <h3 class="info-header">RETURN</h3>
            <div class="container login-info-container" style="margin-bottom: 2vh;">
                <p class="p-info">
                    Your User ID is stored in this browser with a cookie, so whenever you go to <a href="/">play-wuddle.com</a> your progress
                    <span style="font-weight: bold;">will be remembered!</span> See all your ongoing games in the <a href="/">home page</a> and <a href="/create">create more</a> whenever you want.
                </p>
                <p class="p-info">
                    Want to open your account on another device? Simply navigate to the <a href="/">home page</a> and enter your Player Code under 'Sign in'.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>


